2. The 10th day of January 2025 is appointed as the day on which section 
19 of the Public Health (Alcohol) Act 2018 (No. 24 of 2018) comes into 
operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

13 November, 2023. 

STEPHEN DONNELLY, 
Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 17th November, 2023.
